7:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Claude and Perplexity share a solid foundation of core features including Web Search, File Upload, Image Generation, Api Access. Where Claude pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Code Execution and Memory, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on these capabilities. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Claude holds an overall score of 9/10 and an ease of use score of 9/10, while Perplexity scores 8/10 overall and 9/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
8:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, both Claude and Perplexity offer flexible pricing models. Both platforms offer free plans, which is great for testing before committing. Claude's free tier and Perplexity's free tier each have their own limitations, so it is worth evaluating both to see which free offering better matches your initial needs."}]]}]
